{"word":"πλοκή","slug":"πλοκή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πλοκή</b></el> <el>(πλοκή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πλέκω'><el>πλέκω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a twining: anything woven, a web</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>the complication of</i> a plot, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>λύσις</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}